The bug is that `setSpriteFrame('hero_run.png')` expects the frame to already be in `cc.spriteFrameCache`, but no atlas/plist was loaded. The sprite was created from a standalone image file, not from the sprite frame cache.

Fix option 1 — Load frames into cache first:
